Subject: [PATCH 06/10] =?UTF-8?q?dma:=20jz4780:=20=E4=BF=AE=E5=A4=8D=20tx?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=5Fstatus=20NULL=20=E6=8C=87=E9=92=88=E5=B4=A9=E6=BA=83?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

jz4780_dma_tx_status 中 jzchan->desc 可能为 NULL,
导致 aplay 播放时 kernel oops (BadVA=0x00000000).
添加 NULL 检查.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Fable 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
 drivers/dma/dma-jz4780.c | 3 ++-
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/dma/dma-jz4780.c b/drivers/dma/dma-jz4780.c
index 6070dfdb7..614f18d07 100644
--- a/drivers/dma/dma-jz4780.c
+++ b/drivers/dma/dma-jz4780.c
@@ -658,7 +658,8 @@ static enum dma_status jz4780_dma_tx_status(struct dma_chan *chan,
 		/* On the issued list, so hasn't been processed yet */
 		residue = jz4780_dma_desc_residue(jzchan,
 					to_jz4780_dma_desc(vdesc), 0);
-	} else if (cookie == jzchan->desc->vdesc.tx.cookie) {
+	} else if (jzchan->desc &&
+		   cookie == jzchan->desc->vdesc.tx.cookie) {
 		residue = jz4780_dma_desc_residue(jzchan, jzchan->desc,
 					jzchan->curr_hwdesc + 1);
 	}
